This LICENSE governs the Vision source code in the `ncconv/` directory
(Noise-Conditioned Convolution + temporal NC-SSM for degraded-vision
perception), targeted at ICCV 2027 / BMVC 2026 / ACCV 2026 / CVPR 2027
and IEEE TIP 2027. For the repository-wide NC-SSM audio license, see
the root-level LICENSE file. Where the two licenses cover the same
artifact, this LICENSE controls for code under `ncconv/`.

